title: Intervention S02E07 - Follow-Up Christine, Brooks, Ian, Audrey
description:
Remember your favorite addicts? Intervention does!
Watch
Christine, the one that drinks 24oz beers on the train on her way to work at a job that she somehow still has
Brooks and Ian, the brothers that do allllll the drugs. Ian, a handi-capable millionaire, and his cornrowed brother do the whole recovery with Jesus thing.
Audrey, the one that sexed the old guy for crack money!
